<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>rdyt ạlmslwb .. yạ ạ̹lhnạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- rdyt ạlmslwb yạ ạ̹lhnạ bqwẗ ṣlbk
 wạlʿdw mgẖlwb yạ ạ̹lhnạ bslṭạn dmk
 bạlwʿd ạlmktwb yạ ạ̹lhnạ ạ̉nt sẖfạỷnạ
 bạldm ạlmsfwk yạ ạ̹lhnạ nʿln nṣrnạ
 ạlqrạr - nrfʿ ṣwt ạlḥmd lạsmk bạlgẖny̱ wạltsbyḥ
 nʿln ạ̉nh lys mtẖlk ạlḥml ạldẖbyḥ
 nʿln ạ̉nt ạllh wḥdk yswʿ ạlmsyḥ
 2- kạljbạr ạ̉kẖrj yạ ạ̹lhnạ ạ̉nhḍ gẖyrtk
 kạljbạr tqld syfk ạ̉ʿln qwtk
 qd bạd ạlʿạty̱ yạ ạ̹lhnạ bnạr nfkẖtk
 wsby̱ ạljbạr yạ ạ̹lhnạ ṣạr gẖnymtk
 3- dy̱ blạdnạ blạdk yạ ạ̹lhnạ wkẖyrk mạlyhạ
 mạ yswdhạ gẖyrk yạ ạ̹lhnạ wwʿwdk lyhạ
 ttbdl mdẖạbḥ ạ̉wtẖạnhạ bmdẖbḥ lk fyhạ
 lmạ tmd ạ̉ydyk yạ ạ̹lhnạ wtʿrf wsṭyhạ</lyrics>
